            <bug_when>2009-05-11 13:39:44 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>It would be an advantage if we could test the shutdown of each application to monitor missing destruct definitions.

To get the output of these warnings one needs to add the &quot;qx.disposerDebugLevel&quot; setting with a value of at least &quot;1&quot;.

--snip--
&quot;settings&quot; :
{
  &quot;qx.disposerDebugLevel&quot; : &quot;1&quot;
}
--snip--

To manually shutdown an application use

--snip--
qx.core.ObjectRegistry.shutdown();
--snip--</thetext>
          </long_desc>
