            <bug_when>2009-08-31 17:19:50 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>The testing framework is now able to insert custom job configurations into an application&#39;s config.json. This allows automated building of demo apps with the qx.disposerDebugLevel setting. With the option &quot;disposerDebug=true&quot;, Simulations will shut down the AUT at the end of a regular test run and log the disposer debug messages so they will be included in the test report.
A test script that does all this for the demo apps and components is scheduled to run every Sunday at noon.</thetext>
